<br>
Yellow: You can only cast it on yourself.<br>
Red: You can cast it on your current target.<br>
Green: The spell affects anyone close to your target.<br>
Blue: The spell has no range, and will radiate out from you.<br>
Orange: The spell only summons items and doesn't affect anyone.<br>
Purple: You can cast it on everyone in your group.<br>
